[
  "Ben Silbermann is cofounder and the CEO of the photo bookmarking site Pinterest, which went public in April 2019.",
  "Silbermann owns a 38% stake in the company, which had 454 million users worldwide as of June 2021.",
  "Silbermann, along with cofounders Evan Sharp and Paul Sciarra, launched the first desktop version of Pinterest in March 2010.  ",
  "Pinterest lets users save and share image collections from recipes to hairstyles to crafts and home decor through their mobile phones or computers."
]